text: Sky Wu (born 23 July 1966) is a Taiwanese Mandopop singer. He began singing in 1986, and has won two Golden Melody Awards, best new artist in 1990, and best Mandarin male vocalist in 2004. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1966 births Category:Musicians from New Taipei Category:Living people Category:Taiwanese Mandopop singer-songwriters Category:20th-century Taiwanese singers Category:21st-century Taiwanese singers Category:Taiwanese male singers Category:20th-century male singers Category:21st-century male singers
